WEBVTT

00:07:58.640 --> 00:08:03.416
if we just ate less meat
and fed less of the crops to animals,

00:08:03.440 --> 00:08:05.856
there is enough food for everybody

00:08:05.880 --> 00:08:10.200
as long as we think of ourselves
as one group of people.

00:08:12.120 --> 00:08:13.400
And we also know

00:08:15.280 --> 00:08:17.336
about what we do

00:08:17.360 --> 00:08:19.920
so terribly badly nowadays.

00:08:21.480 --> 00:08:26.320
You will have seen this map
of the world before.

00:08:27.480 --> 00:08:29.416
This is the map

00:08:29.440 --> 00:08:32.816
produced by taking satellite images,